page.title: 03Bletchley Teenage Fashion
page.content: In Milton Keynes we have different fashion.There are a group of people called casuals who wear labelled named clothes.These are like Lacoste, Ellesse and Nike.These are very expensive.An Ellessee T shirt could cost over Â£35.A whole suit of all different could cost over Â£100. There is another group of people called Mods.Their clothes aren't as dear as the Casuals.They wear things like Fred Perry jumpers,T shirts and tight trousers.The girls wear mini skirts and ski-pants.They also wear long green coats with pop group names on the back. Another group is the Punks.They wear outrageous clothes like holey T shirts and trousers.They waer belts and studs on their jeans.Their hair is all spiky and many different colours like pink & blue.They also wear lots of earrings.
